{"tid":1264963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撚犬只係宣洩情緒 唔好將重心放晒落去","createTime":"2019-06-29T03:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T03:18:52.000Z","uid":269125,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d7e44c9cee3d214dcf7026e19e119036d3bb01","tid":1264963,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"要集中返3個最迫切既問題先，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">日日撚犬只會嚇走中間派同淺藍</span></strong>，要認清佢地係今次運動功不可抹。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 釋放義士（肥仔聰話有５位被控，一個都不能放棄）<br />\n2. 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n3. 停止人臉識別計劃（個個都要帶身分證出街，點解仲要人臉識別？）</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於撤回取代暫緩，老實講依家靠呢句真係動員力不足，可以繼續作為綱要，但同樣唔應該放太多精力。"},{"pid":"2a83e84c4ae1e9b1238cf1d895bf509f7eceb504","tid":1264963,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"屌犬都要有技巧<br />\n要引到佢地犯錯"},{"pid":"820acf7309f35ff68b4431045f238a323d601dc1","tid":1264963,"uid":269125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a83e84c4ae1e9b1238cf1d895bf509f7eceb504","tid":1264963,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"屌犬都要有技巧<br />\n要引到佢地犯錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:13:49.000Z","msg":"啱，但唔係成日去狗屋講粗口<br />\n無咩意義，因為狗隻已經唔識聽人話"},{"pid":"47d878c2be99f73a3f197be21c108f475afd90e7","tid":1264963,"uid":52621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:15:14.000Z","msg":"咩屌人老婆真心ON9<br />\n我唔係狗都笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c96063509b3e30565e5935582d171401bb684b","tid":1264963,"uid":119494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"撚佢地又如何 <br />\n民心歸我地 驚撚"},{"pid":"4c2203d498e9a5848bae40a29447f19ddf3619d6","tid":1264963,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57c96063509b3e30565e5935582d171401bb684b","tid":1264963,"uid":119494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"撚佢地又如何 <br />\n民心歸我地